MainActivity:
    - Inherit from ComponentActivity

    onCreate method:
        - Call super.onCreate
        - Use setContent to define the UI layout
        - Apply HelloAndroidTheme
        - Inside the theme, call Greeting function with "Android"

Greeting function (Composable):
    - Accept a string parameter called name
    - Display "Hello, name!" as text on the screen

GreetingPreview function (Composable):
    - Apply HelloAndroidTheme
    - Call Greeting with "Android" to show a preview
